hopobject.body: Looking for work enhance pandora Rajeev Chand, managing director at Rutberg & Co., told the Wall Street Journal that the mobile industry appears to be "rooting" for Motorola to swoop in and break up the "duopoly" that currently exists. But he also cautions that pundits, manufacturers, and component suppliers – to name a few – are a bit worried that Motorola's offerings might not be unique enough to carve the company enough space in the wireless world.
